## Module Map

```
:aos-sdk             infrastructure (git submodule, pinned to v<x.y.z>)
:core                contracts (TenantContext, Session, Repository interfaces, Policy interfaces, MVI base)
:design-system       theme + <YourOrgPrefix>* primitives
:data                Fintech*Api family + repository implementations
:features            Logic-Blind UI (packages: auth/, dashboard/, <your-feature>/)
:features-<name>     heavy-SDK or tenant-locked features (if any — chatbot, kyc, support-chat, branch-locator)
:tenants:<region>:base       regional baseline policies (currency, calendar, OTP channel)
:tenants:<region>:default    sentinel tenant for tests
:tenants:<region>:<slug>     concrete tenant — TenantContext factory + @TenantKey bindings
:app                 orchestrator: Application, BootCoordinator, LoggedInComponent, TenantResolverModule
```

Forbidden import edges and the full DAG are in [`framework-rules/RULES.md`](framework-rules/RULES.md) §3.

